==English==
===Alternative spellings===
*[[doggie bag]]

===Etymology===
Diminutive of [[dog]], used attributively with [[bag]]; in the case of the former definition, this is on the notion that the food is to be taken home for the diner's dog

===Noun===
'''[[doggy]] [[bag]]''' (plural [[doggy bags]])
#A [[bag]] (or other [[container]]) used to take home uneaten [[food]] from a restaurant meal
#A bag used to pick up the [[droppings]] of [[dogs]] in [[parks]] and public places